{"tid":948613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"灣仔利景酒店命案男死女昏迷 兩人有家室疑被揭發服藥殉情","createTime":"2018-12-20T08:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T01:24:00.000Z","uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"afefc27f79c1474a9eb3cbf30ed344d7079b7725","tid":948613,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:01:02.000Z","msg":"一對中年男女早上在灣仔道一間酒店被發現昏迷房內，男子證實死亡，女子送院搶救。案件由灣仔重案組第一隊接手調查。據了解，警員在酒店房間內找到藥物，初步不排除二人曾服藥。據稱，兩人均逾60歲，各有家室，疑近日被揭發親密關係，女方曾透露萌死念，昨晚未有回家，家人已報警，警方不排除兩人協議自殺殉情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1In1KQZRjB8SL2ppb_BNDw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20181220a114142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1In1KQZRjB8SL2ppb_BNDw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20181220a114142.jpg&h=89cdf295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場為灣仔道209號利景酒店，職員早上10時48分報警求助。救護員接報到場，證實男子已當場死亡，女子昏迷送律敦治醫院搶救後，留醫深切治療部。<br />\n<br />\n警方正調查兩人的關係。據悉，警方在現場檢獲少量藥物。"},{"pid":"6bee9711c0d2b0b1a6e4844dbb0c94556abc55bd","tid":948613,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"張德蘭教唆自殺"},{"pid":"4e17346e79b515faff2c1aac15e522dc26431b7f","tid":948613,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:05:06.000Z","msg":"成6張野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824ab74b88ff21b7dc13bb9da6613c8ef60427bb","tid":948613,"uid":217538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:11:00.000Z","msg":"失樂園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9ba89984ab04f12581ad438ad20325f5aee00b","tid":948613,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e17346e79b515faff2c1aac15e522dc26431b7f","tid":948613,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-